  <section class="container-shell pt-12">
    <div class="panel p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Collaboration framing</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
        Novalink supports scoped projects and ongoing execution support. Typical starting points include websites, landing pages, commerce/payment implementation, search support, and selected automation-focused work.
      </p>
